{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01KufzyxaAvuA6ZJDE5Nj8jv","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01DzMzKcLkDLoQLJzQcjhT4w","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cat > /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/ota_foldcasc.spice << 'EOF'\n* VibroSense Folded-Cascode OTA\n* Topology: NMOS input pair, PMOS fold + cascode, NMOS cascode + current source\n* Per program.md Section 3.3-3.4\n*\n* Ports: vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n*   vinp/vinn = differential input\n*   vout      = single-ended output\n*   vdd/vss   = supply rails\n*   vbn       = NMOS current source gate bias (M9/M10/M11)\n*   vbcn      = NMOS cascode gate bias (M7/M8)\n*   vbp       = PMOS fold/current source gate bias (M3/M4)\n*   vbcp      = PMOS cascode gate bias (M5/M6)\n\n.subckt ota_foldcasc vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n\n* --- Input differential pair ---\n* M1 (input+): drain=fold_p, gate=vinp, source=tail, body=vss\nM1 fold_p vinp tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 w=10u l=1u nf=2\n* M2 (input-): drain=fold_n, gate=vinn, source=tail, body=vss\nM2 fold_n vinn tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 w=10u l=1u nf=2\n\n* --- Tail current source ---\n* M11: drain=tail, gate=vbn, source=vss, body=vss\nM11 tail vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 w=4u l=4u nf=1\n\n* --- PMOS fold transistors (current sources from VDD) ---\n* M3 (fold+): drain=fold_p, gate=vbp, source=src3, body=vdd\nM3 fold_p vbp src3 vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 w=8u l=1u nf=2\n* M4 (fold-): drain=fold_n, gate=vbp, source=src4, body=vdd\nM4 fold_n vbp src4 vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 w=8u l=1u nf=2\n\n* --- PMOS bias mirrors (top current sources) ---\n* M12: drain=src3, gate=vbp, source=vdd, body=vdd\nM12 src3 vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 w=8u l=2u nf=1\n* M13: drain=src4, gate=vbp, source=vdd, body=vdd\nM13 src4 vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 w=8u l=2u nf=1\n\n* --- PMOS cascode ---\n* M5 (cascode+): drain=cas_p, gate=vbcp, source=fold_p, body=vdd\nM5 cas_p vbcp fold_p vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 w=8u l=0.5u nf=2\n* M6 (cascode-): drain=vout, gate=vbcp, source=fold_n, body=vdd\nM6 vout vbcp fold_n vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 w=8u l=0.5u nf=2\n\n* --- NMOS cascode ---\n* M7 (cascode+): drain=cas_p, gate=vbcn, source=src7, body=vss\nM7 cas_p vbcn src7 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 w=4u l=0.5u nf=2\n* M8 (cascode-): drain=vout, gate=vbcn, source=src8, body=vss\nM8 vout vbcn src8 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 w=4u l=0.5u nf=2\n\n* --- NMOS current sources ---\n* M9: drain=src7, gate=vbn, source=vss, body=vss\nM9 src7 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 w=4u l=2u nf=1\n* M10: drain=src8, gate=vbn, source=vss, body=vss\nM10 src8 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 w=4u l=2u nf=1\n\n.ends ota_foldcasc\nEOF\necho \"Created ota_foldcasc.spice\"","description":"Create OTA subcircuit"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":525,"cache_read_input_tokens":113326,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":525},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"37d800be-0a8d-4fa4-9160-013da436175b","uuid":"21a4303c-847c-4512-944e-58e0b39c84ae"}
