{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01EPh7kgkhWLbYABLv9ump2j","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_011u2VzoMyZoYFocw2jxLQav","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cat > /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/ota_foldcasc.spice << 'EOF'\n* VibroSense Folded-Cascode OTA — SKY130A\n* Topology per program.md Section 3.3\n* Uses raw BSIM4 model names (M-prefix) for verifier compatibility\n*\n* Ports: vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n\n.subckt ota_foldcasc vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n\n* --- Input Differential Pair ---\nM1 fold_p vinp tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=10u L=1u nf=2\nM2 fold_n vinn tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=10u L=1u nf=2\n\n* --- Tail Current Source ---\nM11 tail vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=4u L=4u nf=1\n\n* --- PMOS Fold/Current Sources from VDD ---\nM3  fold_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=1u nf=2\nM4  fold_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=1u nf=2\n\n* --- PMOS Bias Mirrors (parallel with M3/M4) ---\nM12 fold_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=2u nf=1\nM13 fold_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=2u nf=1\n\n* --- PMOS Cascode ---\nM5  cas_p vbcp fold_p vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=0.5u nf=2\nM6  vout  vbcp fold_n vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=0.5u nf=2\n\n* --- NMOS Cascode ---\nM7  cas_p vbcn src7 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=4u L=0.5u nf=2\nM8  vout  vbcn src8 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=4u L=0.5u nf=2\n\n* --- NMOS Current Sources (sized for 250nA each) ---\nM9  src7 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=2u L=4u nf=1\nM10 src8 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=2u L=4u nf=1\n\n.ends ota_foldcasc\nEOF\necho \"Created ota_foldcasc.spice\"","description":"Create corrected OTA with right M9/M10 sizing"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_to