{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_015ggueV29rbmfBDrzFS4krV","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01QBCH2HFxpJgsqG2DF98VTt","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cat > /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/ota_foldcasc.spice << 'EOF'\n* VibroSense Folded-Cascode OTA — SKY130A\n* Sized for SKY130 PMOS |Vth|~1.0V, NMOS Vth~0.6V\n* All devices must be in moderate inversion (Vov > 150mV PMOS, >50mV NMOS signal)\n\n.subckt ota_foldcasc vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n\n* --- Input Differential Pair (small W for Vov > 50mV at ~500nA) ---\nXM1 fold_p vinp tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=0.84u L=1u nf=1\nXM2 fold_n vinn tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=0.84u L=1u nf=1\n\n* --- Tail Current Source ---\nXM11 tail vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=4u L=4u nf=1\n\n* --- PMOS Fold/Current Sources (small W/L for Vov > 150mV at ~500nA) ---\nXM3  fold_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.84u L=4u nf=1\nXM4  fold_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.84u L=4u nf=1\n\n* --- PMOS Bias Mirrors ---\nXM12 fold_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=4u nf=1\nXM13 fold_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=4u nf=1\n\n* --- PMOS Cascode ---\nXM5  cas_p vbcp fold_p vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\nXM6  vout  vbcp fold_n vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\n\n* --- NMOS Cascode ---\nXM7  cas_p vbcn src7 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=0.5u nf=1\nXM8  vout  vbcn src8 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=0.5u nf=1\n\n* --- NMOS Current Sources ---\nXM9  src7 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u nf=1\nXM10 src8 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u nf=1\n\n.ends ota_foldcasc\nEOF\necho \"Updated OTA with SKY130-appropriate sizing\"","description":"Update OTA with correct sizing for SKY130"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1081,"cache_read_i