{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01LgP64MDYamHjyRvBPmcJtE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_016onvvWfuuF4K6UbVrNYm3a","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cat > /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/ota_foldcasc.spice << 'EOF'\n* VibroSense Folded-Cascode OTA — SKY130A\n* Sized for Vov constraints: PMOS>150mV, NMOS signal>50mV\n\n.subckt ota_foldcasc vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n\n* Input Differential Pair (W=0.42u for Vov>50mV at 300nA)\nXM1 fold_p vinp tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\nXM2 fold_n vinn tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\n\n* Tail Current Source (~600nA)\nXM11 tail vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=4u L=4u nf=1\n\n* PMOS Fold (W=0.42u L=1u, ~500nA at Vov=150mV)\nXM3  fold_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\nXM4  fold_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\n\n* PMOS Bias Mirrors (small, ~60nA)\nXM12 fold_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=8u nf=1\nXM13 fold_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=8u nf=1\n\n* PMOS Cascode (W=0.42u L=2u for Vov>150mV at ~250nA)\nXM5  cas_p vbcp fold_p vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=2u nf=1\nXM6  vout  vbcp fold_n vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=2u nf=1\n\n* NMOS Cascode\nXM7  cas_p vbcn src7 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=0.5u nf=1\nXM8  vout  vbcn src8 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=0.5u nf=1\n\n* NMOS Current Sources (~250nA mirror ratio ~0.4 of M11)\nXM9  src7 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=5u nf=1\nXM10 src8 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=5u nf=1\n\n.ends ota_foldcasc\nEOF\n\ncat > /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/debug.spice << 'EOF'\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\nVdd nvdd 0 dc 1.8\nV0 ngnd 0 dc 0\nVbn nbn 0 dc 0.59\nVbcn nbcn 0 dc 0.75\nVbp nbp 0 dc 0.73\nVbcp nbcp 0 dc 0.40\nVinp ninp 0 dc 0.9\nVinn ninn 0 dc 0.9\n\nXota ninp ninn nout nvdd ngnd nbn nbcn nbp nbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL nout 0 10p\n\n.nodeset v(nout)=0.9 v(xota.fold_p)=1.4 v(xota.fold_n)=1.4\n.nodeset v(xota.cas_p)=0.9 v(xota.tail)=0.3 v(xota.src7)=0.2 v(xota.src8)=0.2\n\n.op\n.control\nrun\necho \"\"\necho \"========== OPERATING POINT SUMMARY ==========\"\nforeach dev m1 m2 m3 m4 m5 m6 m7 m8 m9 m10 m11 m12 m13\n  * Use different model names for NMOS vs PMOS\nend\n\n* Print all key params manually\necho \"=== M11 (tail NMOS) ===\"\nprint @m.xota.xm11.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[id] @m.xota.xm11.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[vgs] @m.xota.xm11.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[vth] @m.xota.xm11.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[vds] @m.xota.xm11.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[vdsat]\necho \"=== M1 (input NMOS) ===\"\nprint @m.xota.xm1.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[id] @m.xota.xm1.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[vgs] @m.xota.xm1.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[vth] @m.xota.xm1.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[vds] @m.xota.xm1.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[vdsat]\necho \"=== M2 (input NMOS) ===\"\nprint @m.xota.xm2.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[id] @m.xota.xm2.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[vgs] @m.xota.xm2.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[vth] @m.xota.xm2.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[vds] @m.xota.xm2.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[vdsat]\necho \"=== M3 (fold PMOS) ===\"\nprint @m.xota.xm3.msky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8[id] @m.xota.xm3.msky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8[vgs] @m.xota.xm3.msky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8[vth] @m.xota.xm3.msky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8[vds] @m.xota.xm3.msky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8[vdsat]\necho \"=== M4 (fold PMOS) ===\"\nprint @m.xota.xm4.msky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8[id] @m.xota.xm4.msky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8[vgs] @m.xota.xm4.msky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8[vth] @m.xota.xm4.msky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8[vds] @m.xota.xm4.msky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8[vdsat]\necho \"=== M5 (PMOS cascode) ===\"\nprint @m.xota.xm5.msky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8[id] @m.xota.xm5.msky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8[vgs] @m.xota.xm5.msky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8[vth] @m.xota.xm5.msky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8[vds] @m.xota.xm5.msky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8[vdsat]\necho \"=== M6 (PMOS cascode) ===\"\