{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01PGCEwDku9wfNZoULHx9VMn","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01VkWP1o6WL23ZQ67Be63vD5","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cat > /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/ota_foldcasc.spice << 'EOF'\n* VibroSense Folded-Cascode OTA — SKY130A v5\n* 2µA total, all PMOS at Vov≈150mV in saturation\n\n.subckt ota_foldcasc vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n\n* Input Pair (W=0.42u L=1u, 500nA each → Vov≈90mV)\nXM1 fold_p vinp tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\nXM2 fold_n vinn tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\n\n* Tail (1µA)\nXM11 tail vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=4u L=4u nf=1\n\n* PMOS Fold (W=0.42u L=1u, ~500nA at Vov≈150mV)\nXM3  fold_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\nXM4  fold_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\n\n* PMOS Bias Mirrors (same as M3/M4 for ~500nA each)\nXM12 fold_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\nXM13 fold_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\n\n* PMOS Cascode (W=0.42u L=1u for ~500nA at Vov≈150mV)\nXM5  cas_p vbcp fold_p vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\nXM6  vout  vbcp fold_n vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\n\n* NMOS Cascode (W=0.42u L=1u, 500nA → Vov≈90mV)\nXM7  cas_p vbcn src7 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\nXM8  vout  vbcn src8 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=0.42u L=1u nf=1\n\n* NMOS Current Sources (500nA, mirror ratio 0.5 of M11)\nXM9  src7 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u nf=1\nXM10 src8 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=4u nf=1\n\n.ends ota_foldcasc\nEOF\n\n# Also update tb_ota_op.spice with correct Vbn\n# Need Vbn for M11≈1µA (from sweep, ~0.62V)\nsed -i 's/Vbn  vbn  0 dc 0.59/Vbn  vbn  0 dc 0.621/' /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/tb_ota_op.spice\n\n# Adjust Vbcp: for M5 in saturation, need Vsg≈1.07V.\n# fold_p ≈ 1.62V: Vbcp