{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01GWrT2bJL68DLUAdXhe8shv","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01MNjZT1CTnFziCgs6smnZ6G","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cat > /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/tb_ota_ac.spice << 'EOF'\n* TB01: AC Open-Loop Analysis (Section 6.1)\n* Measures DC gain, UGB, phase margin\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\n.param vdd_val = 1.8\n.param vcm_val = 0.9\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc {vdd_val}\n\n* Bias voltages (same as tb_ota_op)\nVbn  vbn  0 dc 0.59\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\nVbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\n\n* DC bias at mid-rail, AC stimulus on positive input\nVinp vinp 0 dc {vcm_val} ac 1\nVinn vinn 0 dc {vcm_val}\n\n* OTA open-loop with DC stabilization\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n* DC stabilization (same as OP testbench)\nRbias1 vout vmid 1e6\nRbias2 xota.cas_p vmid 1e6\nVmid vmid 0 dc {vcm_val}\n\n.nodeset v(vout)=0.9 v(xota.cas_p)=0.9\n\n* AC analysis\n.ac dec 100 0.1 1G\n\n* Measurements expected by verifier\n.meas ac gain_peak MAX vdb(vout)\n.meas ac g1 FIND vdb(vout) AT=1\n.meas ac g10 FIND vdb(vout) AT=10\n.meas ac g100 FIND vdb(vout) AT=100\n.meas ac ugb WHEN vdb(vout)=0 FALL=1\n.meas ac phase_ugb FIND vp(vout) WHEN vdb(vout)=0 FALL=1\n\n.end\nEOF\necho \"Created tb_ota_ac.spice\"","description":"Create AC testbench"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":469,"cache_read_input_tokens":297878,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":469},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"37d800be-0a8d-4fa4-9160-013da436175b","uuid":"cb37ed08-2a03-4355-ba70-42e0a5a8f042"}
