{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_016T3rVffLbsVYP14oZU4KQX","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_011p2nbxVJMyWtsUz3kJQvHL","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"# Build DC sweep testbench (Section 6.2)\ncat > /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/tb_ota_dc.spice << 'EOF'\n* TB02: DC Sweep — Output swing measurement\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\n.param vdd_val = 1.8\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc {vdd_val}\n\n* Bias voltages\nVbn  vbn  0 dc 0.59\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\nVbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\n\n* Unity-gain feedback: vout → vinn\nVinp vinp 0 dc 0.9\nXota vinp vout vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.dc Vinp 0 1.8 0.001\n\n.control\nrun\nmeas dc vout_max MAX v(vout)\nmeas dc vout_min MIN v(vout)\n\necho \"vout_max = $&vout_max\"\necho \"vout_min = $&vout_min\"\nquit\n.endc\n.end\nEOF\n\n# Build Transient step response testbench (Section 6.3)\ncat > /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/tb_ota_tran.spice << 'EOF'\n* TB03: Transient Step Response — Slew rate measurement\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\n.param vdd_val = 1.8\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc {vdd_val}\n\n* Bias voltages\nVbn  vbn  0 dc 0.59\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\nVbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\n\n* Unity-gain feedback with 100mV step at t=10us\nVinp vinp 0 dc 0.9 PULSE(0.9 1.0 10u 1n 1n 50u 100u)\nXota vinp vout vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.tran 10n 100u\n\n.control\nrun\n* Measure 10% and 90% of step (0.9V to 1.0V, so 10%=0.91, 90%=0.99)\n* The verifier computes SR from t10 and t90\nmeas tran t10 WHEN v(vout)=0.91 RISE=1\nmeas tran t90 WHEN v(vout)=0.99 RISE=1\n\necho \"t10 = $&t10\"\necho \"t90 = $&t90\"\nquit\n.endc\n.end\nEOF\n\necho \"Created tb_ota_dc.spice and tb_ota_tran.spice\"\npython3 verify_design.py 2>&1 | grep -E \"GATE|RESULT|swing|Slew|FAIL|PASS\" | head -20","description":"Build and test Gate 3 testbenches","timeout":300000},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":542,"cache_read_input_tokens":316935,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":542},"output_tokens":40,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"37d800be-0a8d-4fa4-9160-013da436175b","uuid":"f8e562f9-2f86-413c-bd46-a166343aa0d0"}
