{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01RSUV9Yf9F8E3AaG7nPd8Na","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01PBNrCJnVRPjKeNAS7Mc76N","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cat > /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/tb_ota_tran.spice << 'EOF'\n* TB03: Transient Step Response — Slew rate\n* Uses unity-gain with 100mV step per spec\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc 1.8\nVbn  vbn  0 dc 0.59\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\nVbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\n\n* 100mV step at t=10us in unity-gain feedback\nVinp vinp 0 PULSE(0.9 1.0 10u 1n 1n 50u 100u)\nXota vinp vout vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.tran 1n 100u\n\n.control\nrun\n\n* Measure initial slope (derivative method) as a proxy for SR\n* The verifier needs t10 and t90 format\n* Use derivative at 50% crossing\nmeas tran v_before FIND v(vout) AT=9.9u\nmeas tran v_after FIND v(vout) AT=50u\n\nlet step = v_after - v_before\nlet v_10 = v_before + 0.1 * step\nlet v_90 = v_before + 0.9 * step\n\nmeas tran t10_val WHEN v(vout)=$&v_10 RISE=1\nmeas tran t90_val WHEN v(vout)=$&v_90 RISE=1\n\necho \"t10 = $&t10_val\"\necho \"t90 = $&t90_val\"\nquit\n.endc\n.end\nEOF\npython3 verify_design.py 2>&1 | grep -E \"GATE|RESULT|Slew|PASS|FAIL|ALL\" | head -10","description":"Test with finer timestep","timeout":300000},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2387,"cache_read_input_tokens":331985,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2387},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"37d800be-0a8d-4fa4-9160-013da436175b","uuid":"f1963451-a2a7-4df5-a1e5-f9e9d871bb92"}
